dc_title_s: Nieuwe afteekening van het eyland Spits-Bergen opgegeven door de commandeurs Giles en Outger Rep, en in't ligt gebragt en uytgegeven door Gerard van Keulen
dc_description_s: Facsimile of historical Dutch and English maps of Spitsbergen and other Svalbard islands. Dates and approximate locations of Dutch and English discoveries are shown. Keulen map includes major icebergs. Relief shown by hachures. Depth shown by soundings and pictorially. Purchas map includes illustrations of watercraft, marine life, and terrestrial mammals. From: The Journal of the Royal Geographical Society of London. Vol. 43 (1873), pp. 83-97; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J687 v. 43 1873
dc_subject_sm: Spitsbergen Island (Norway)—Description and travel—Early works to 1800
